These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
Beverage: coffee, fanta, water, iced-tea
Hobby: writing, chess, collecting, card-games
1. Beverage:fanta is between Beverage:coffee and Hobby:chess##2
2. Beverage:fanta is on the left or right of Hobby:writing##3
3. Beverage:fanta is somewhere between Beverage:iced-tea and Beverage:coffee##7
4. Hobby:chess is in an even position##4
5. Beverage:iced-tea is on the right of Hobby:collecting##1
6. Hobby:chess is somewhere to the left of Hobby:writing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | water | iced-tea       | fanta | coffee        |
| Hobby      | collecting  | chess | card-games        | writing |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
Pet: ferret, fish, chinchilla, guinea-pig
Sport: handball, sailing, cricket, golf
1. Sport:golf is somewhere between Sport:cricket and Pet:chinchilla##7
2. Pet:guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of Pet:ferret##5
3. Pet:guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of Sport:golf##5
4. Pet:fish is on the left of Pet:guinea-pig##1
5. Sport:golf is between Sport:cricket and Sport:sailing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | chinchilla | fish       | guinea-pig         | ferret     |
| Sport   | sailing   | golf | cricket | handball |

