.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
Movie-Genre: martial-arts, superhero, satire, western
Music-Genre: hip-hop, electronic, d&b, salsa
1. Movie-Genre:martial-arts is on the right of Music-Genre:salsa##1
2. Music-Genre:salsa is somewhere between Music-Genre:electronic and Music-Genre:hip-hop##7
3. Music-Genre:d&b is on the left of Movie-Genre:western##1
4. Music-Genre:hip-hop is somewhere between Music-Genre:salsa and Movie-Genre:superhero##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | western | satire | martial-arts  |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | hip-hop  | salsa   | electronic |

