.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
Hobby: baking, fishing, filmmaking, camping
Sport: ice-hockey, baseball, cricket, swimming
1. Sport:swimming is on the far left or far right##3
2. Hobby:baking is somewhere between Sport:baseball and Hobby:camping##7
3. Hobby:filmmaking == Sport:swimming##1
4. Sport:cricket is on the left of Sport:swimming##1
5. Hobby:fishing is on the left of Sport:ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | fishing | baking | camping       | filmmaking |
| Sport   | baseball      | ice-hockey   | cricket | swimming  |

