5. Nationality:nigerian is on the left of Nationality:russian##1
6. Nationality:turkish is somewhere to the left of Nationality:nigerian##5
7. Hobby:fishing is on the far left or far right##3
8. Hobby:cooking is on the left or right of Hobby:hiking##3

.:: Answer ::.
